column2: SELECT o.objid, o.specobjid, o.ra, o.dec, o.petromag_u, o.petromagerr_u, o.petromag_g, o.petromagerr_g, o.petromag_r, o.petromagerr_r, o.petromag_i, o.petromagerr_i, o.petromag_z, o.petromagerr_z into mydb.petromags_Davestudent1 FROM MyDB.MyTable_# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjall AS o ON n.objid = o.objid
